<h3 class="wp-block-heading">The New Whispers</h3>



<p>The change brings simplicity.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>No more Org Mode <code>:PROPERTIES:</code> drawer parsing.</li>



<li>No more Org header traversing.</li>



<li>I changed the metadata in favor of keywords (like <code>#+CATEGORY:</code>).</li>



<li>I removed the unused code.</li>



<li>I installed simplicity. Deployed clarity.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Keywords Are The Soul</h3>



<p>On the top of the Org files &#8211; everything&#8217;s clear.</p>


<div class="wp-block-syntaxhighlighter-code "><pre class="brush: plain; title: ; notranslate">
